entry.title: Russian Proxies in Eastern Ukraine Mobilize Troops, Kill Two Ukrainian Soldiers
entry.content: Russian-installed authorities in Donetsk and Luhansk say an attack by Kyiv is imminent, while shelling across the frontline intensifies, killing two Ukrainian soldiers.

entry.title: Russian Naval Drills Threaten Ukraine's Limited Coastal Defenses
entry.content: The naval exercises in the waters around Ukraine pose a threat to key ports and infrastructure, with the Russian vessels and seaborne missiles potentially playing a key role in an invasion.
